{"tid":303023,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"滙豐報告：港孩教育開支逾百萬　全球最貴！","createTime":"2017-06-29T23:50:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-30T01:02:51.000Z","uid":81228,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0670d93e11ec601160a100cc794c25246611714c","tid":303023,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T23:50:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170629/large/1498727989_9993.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170629%2Flarge%2F1498727989_9993.jpg&h=c5dd5771&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n十一年前，風之后李麗珊話養大一個小朋友要400萬元。滙豐發表調查報告指，今時今日，一個香港小朋友的教育開支就要超過一百萬，在15個國家及地區中位列榜首。<br />\n<br />\n滙豐「教育的價值」系列最新報告《志存高遠》（Higher and higher）顯示，從小學至大學本科階段，香港父母用於子女教育（包括學費、教育書籍、交通及住宿）的總開支是在眾多受訪市場中最貴，達到13.2萬美元，拆合約103萬元（港元‧下同）。<br />\n<br />\n第二貴是阿聯酋，子女教育開支需約77.5萬元，較香港低24.7%；新加坡排第三，子女教育開支約55.3萬元；緊隨其後的是美國（45.6萬）、台灣（44萬）、中國內地（38.2萬），而英國排名第九位（19.4萬）。值得一提的是，全球平均子女教育開支為34.5萬，遠低於香港。<br />\n<br />\n香港最多慈父慈母，報告訪問了15個國家和地區8,400多位家長，88%的受訪香港父母表示現正或曾經支付私人補習費。為支付子女的教育開支，不少香港父母選擇在財務上作出犧牲，包括削減自己的消閒活動開支（50%）。27%的港爸港媽表示，現正或曾經減少自己的長期儲蓄或投資供款，在受訪市場中排列第三。<br />\n<br />\n75%的香港家長以日常收入應付子女的教育開支。19%的香港家長有特設的教育儲蓄或投資計劃作為子女的教育經費，比例低於全球的21%，中國內地的比例則達到43%，是在所有受訪市場中最高。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/finance/20170629/56892725\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Ffinance%2F20170629%2F56892725&d=Lef6mzCXcJ9AA5ymDh00qKWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=22ed9f11\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Ffinance%2F20170629%2F56892725&h=f8157377\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/finance/20170629/56892725</a>"},{"pid":"cdbe36d7def98f69ee61800eb48eaf6aaff1423c","tid":303023,"uid":63,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T23:55:36.000Z","msg":"世界第一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f0d6f5a6e0655fab31e31d1e798fc76f149fb93","tid":303023,"uid":48286,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T23:56:54.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">扮撚曬嘢,  由小學到大學悉心栽培緊係一百萬啦, 幾多支那蝗蟲, 蝻亞賤種，生埋生埋一百幾十竇，天生天養，食政府咬綜援，撚有一百萬， 屌你老母淨係揀中產黎計數，夠薑就拉平均數， 喺度篤數做新聞，再昆鳩人買升學基金<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n[size=1]持有匯豐控股/size=1]"},{"pid":"6644412683e3e90fea7d3c616acf1ca46ecd1759","tid":303023,"uid":99530,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T00:15:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170629/large/1498727989_9993.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170629%2Flarge%2F1498727989_9993.jpg&h=c5dd5771&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n十一年前，風之后李麗珊話養大一個小朋友要400萬元。滙豐發表調查報告指，今時今日，一個香港小朋友的教育開支就要超過一百萬，在15個國家及地區中位列榜首。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/finance/20170629/56892725\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Ffinance%2F20170629%2F56892725&d=Lef6mzCXcJ9AA5ymDh00qKWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=22ed9f11\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Ffinance%2F20170629%2F56892725&h=f8157377\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/finance/20170629/56892725</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nquote李麗珊十一年前句說話搞到成段野好奇怪。<br />\n<br />\n我係expect下半句應該遠超400萬，點知得100萬。"},{"pid":"8df4db42d3778242eba8885ad00f29e915d3e370","tid":303023,"uid":6728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T00:58:29.000Z","msg":"至全睪丸報告<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa16e779865d36546d5a82eac1e0a7022f9c47cc","tid":303023,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T01:02:51.000Z","msg":"啲乜七興趣補習多到仆街貴到離譜,加上班白痴老豆老母,商家笑呵呵"}]}